{"tid":1894603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"肺炎重擊南韓！GFRIEND「已經入座了」簽售會急喊卡","createTime":"2020-02-24T04:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T05:18:58.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5338d96ed4fb2b77aae19195dfec0cf82ba6dafd","tid":1894603,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"南韓女團GFRIEND憑藉整齊劃一的舞蹈動作、唱跳實力，雖然是小公司出身卻熬出高知名度。她們在二月初開始了睽違7個月的回歸，卻沒想到受到新冠肺炎的影響，23日簽售會竟發生讓成員們淚灑舞台的尷尬事件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4718/d4718593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4718%2Fd4718593.jpg&h=d46d4dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND時隔七個月回歸，卻碰上新冠肺炎影響。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n受到新冠肺炎的影響，不少偶像與粉絲近距離的活動都受到影響，像是女團IZ*ONE就戴上了口罩進行簽名會。而差不多時期回歸的GFRIEND，原定在23日舉辦新專輯的簽售會，當天也是她們結束打歌期的日子，雖然南韓疫情大爆發令人心慌，但幸運中獎的粉絲還是不願意錯過與偶像相見的機會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4718/d4718592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4718%2Fd4718592.jpg&h=18c74d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND時隔七個月回歸，卻碰上新冠肺炎影響。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n沒想到當成員和粉絲都入座後，工作人員卻突然宣布，因為新冠肺炎疫情影響，簽售會將延期舉行，當天活動即刻結束。突然急轉直下的巨變不只粉絲震驚，連GFRIEND都嚇一大跳，成員們尷尬又難過得向粉絲道歉，最後更是忍不住淚灑舞台。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mademyday_603B?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1231525156050178049&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1652429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmademyday_603B%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1231525156050178049%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1652429&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6641e20f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mademyday_603B?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1231525156050178049&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1652429</a><br />\n隊長所願擦過眼淚後，拿起麥克風哽咽說道：「真的好可惜⋯」一旁的銀河和老么嚴智更是抱在一起哭了起來，讓粉絲不捨得在台下大喊：「下次再辦就好！」、「不要哭！沒關係的！」影片在韓網傳開後，網友看了也心疼直喊：「居然入座了才說取消？」、「取消不是問題，這時期都能理解的，但實在太突然了。」、「怎麼會讓藝人面對這麼尷尬的情況。」"},{"pid":"05f53d2349808eb41eface0129b1709d9cd3a96d","tid":1894603,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚搞笑 坐低哂準備好先嗌取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4326651d6c8e73e3264bb54275295edeb81c88af","tid":1894603,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DG3VTDd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDG3VTDd.gif&h=301bf362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c86ac623900d12f3f477cbc104bcb35575f146f2","tid":1894603,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"幾時停飛垃圾韓國"},{"pid":"e8cd110e250fd5acd648995072f10cc428cc26c3","tid":1894603,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f53d2349808eb41eface0129b1709d9cd3a96d","tid":1894603,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚搞笑 坐低哂準備好先嗌取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"喜聞樂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541f11948ecb5d8b248f1d3397a138e5693e3623","tid":1894603,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05f53d2349808eb41eface0129b1709d9cd3a96d","tid":1894603,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚搞笑 坐低哂準備好先嗌取消<img src=\"/assets/faces